         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">103  ¶ Logania ovata ¶  RBr (small variety) ¶ Easter morning ¶  ¶ Avoiding all relaxation during the holidays, dear Mr Tepper, I am trying to snatch some free hours to do justice to my correspondents....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">86.04.25</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">103 <name key="Logania%20ovata">Logania ovata</name> RBr (Kleine Var)</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Ostermorgen.</hi>
               </seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The letter is dated to 1886, as the date of collection of Tepper's <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Logonia</seg>, MEL 75458 is given as 1 March 1886 in AVH. In 1886 Easter fell on 25 April, and the letter is dated accordingly.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Indem ich mir alle Erholung während der Festtage entziehe, lieber Herr Tepper, versuche ich einige Freistunden zu erhaschen, um meinen Correspondenten gerecht zu werden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bis jetzt habe ich wenig an Neu Guin. - Pflanz. arbeiten können, doch sind die Austellungs-Arbeiten für London beendigt!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">102. Scheint mir aus den beblätterter Asten von Hibbertia Billardierii u aus einer anklebenden Blume von <name key="Thomasia%20petalocalyx">Thomasia petalocalyx</name> zu bestehen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Frühling liessen sich gewiss noch viele Orchideen u Annuelle finden.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit bestem Grusse der</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">103 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Logania%20ovata">Logania ovata</name>
               </seg> RBr (small variety)</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Easter morning</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Avoiding all relaxation during the holidays, dear Mr Tepper, I am trying to snatch some free hours to do justice to my correspondents.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Up to the present I have been able to work little on New Guinea plants, but the exhibition work for London<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Colonial and Indian Exhibition, London, 1886.</p>
               </note> is finished!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">102. Seems to me to consist of the leafy branches of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Hibbertia%20billardierii">Hibbertia billardierii</name>
               </seg> and of an adhering flower of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Thomasia%20petalocalyx">Thomasia petalocalyx</name>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the spring certainly many orchids and annuals will yet be found.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With best greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Hibbertia%20billardierii">Hibbertia billardierii</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Logania%20ovata">Logania ovata</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Thomasia%20petalocalyx">Thomasia petalocalyx</name>
            </p>
         </div>
